  "detailed_description": "<strong>Embark on a haunting journey in Ontotis, where chilling secrets of the past shape a story that blurs reality and nightmare in this psychological horror experience.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484500/extras/9a8f44b5f634f2de0cfda72e4cfa3245.poster.avif?t=1730737334\" width=542 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484500/extras/9a8f44b5f634f2de0cfda72e4cfa3245.webm?t=1730737334\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484500/extras/9a8f44b5f634f2de0cfda72e4cfa3245.mp4?t=1730737334\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>Key Features</u></strong><br><br>❖  Engage in an immersive gameplay experience that blends an atmospheric environment with chilling horror elements.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484500/extras/74baca84e2e0e4ca835acb0dd1e7733d.poster.avif?t=1730737334\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484500/extras/74baca84e2e0e4ca835acb0dd1e7733d.webm?t=1730737334\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484500/extras/74baca84e2e0e4ca835acb0dd1e7733d.mp4?t=1730737334\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>❖  Solve intricate puzzles to progress the story and unlock secrets.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484500/extras/c426e3bacf7ccd61f5601e458212fefd.poster.avif?t=1730737334\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484500/extras/c426e3bacf7ccd61f5601e458212fefd.webm?t=1730737334\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484500/extras/c426e3bacf7ccd61f5601e458212fefd.mp4?t=1730737334\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>❖  Piece together the mystery by discovering scattered items and pages that hold crucial clues within the game.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484500/extras/5efb189bbc3b7d49b4e85dd076f32c22.poster.avif?t=1730737334\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484500/extras/5efb189bbc3b7d49b4e85dd076f32c22.webm?t=1730737334\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484500/extras/5efb189bbc3b7d49b4e85dd076f32c22.mp4?t=1730737334\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>❖  Explore different endings based on the items used and mysteries unraveled.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484500/extras/7dd4d1e61f474741972a5f8d405ec104.poster.avif?t=1730737334\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484500/extras/7dd4d1e61f474741972a5f8d405ec104.webm?t=1730737334\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484500/extras/7dd4d1e61f474741972a5f8d405ec104.mp4?t=1730737334\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong><u>Story</u></strong><br>You take the role of Robert, a man grappling with the loss of his wife Joann, as he takes on a remote job as a caretaker for abandoned homes during the winter/fall season in search of peace and solitude. However, as a severe storm approaches, you are tasked with securing one final property on the hill. <br>As you secure the house and complete your chores, strange occurrences and unexplained phenomena come to light, along with a mysterious figure that seems linked to the events at hand. <br>Through examination of various objects and clues within the property, you begin to realize that a sinister presence may be at play, leading to a series of unsettling events during your stay as you try to piece together the mystery of the former residents of the house.",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Embark on a haunting journey in Ontotis, where chilling secrets of the past shape a story that blurs reality and nightmare in this psychological horror experience.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484500/extras/9a8f44b5f634f2de0cfda72e4cfa3245.poster.avif?t=1730737334\" width=542 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484500/extras/9a8f44b5f634f2de0cfda72e4cfa3245.webm?t=1730737334\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484500/extras/9a8f44b5f634f2de0cfda72e4cfa3245.mp4?t=1730737334\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>Key Features</u></strong><br><br>❖  Engage in an immersive gameplay experience that blends an atmospheric environment with chilling horror elements.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484500/extras/74baca84e2e0e4ca835acb0dd1e7733d.poster.avif?t=1730737334\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484500/extras/74baca84e2e0e4ca835acb0dd1e7733d.webm?t=1730737334\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484500/extras/74baca84e2e0e4ca835acb0dd1e7733d.mp4?t=1730737334\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>❖  Solve intricate puzzles to progress the story and unlock secrets.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484500/extras/c426e3bacf7ccd61f5601e458212fefd.poster.avif?t=1730737334\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstati