e and solitude. However, as a severe storm approaches, you are tasked with securing one final property on the hill. <br>As you secure the house and complete your chores, strange occurrences and unexplained phenomena come to light, along with a mysterious figure that seems linked to the events at hand. <br>Through examination of various objects and clues within the property, you begin to realize that a sinister presence may be at play, leading to a series of unsettling events during your stay as you try to piece together the mystery of the former residents of the house.",
